data.description: This cozy residence is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, offering a delightful living experience for you and your family. Enjoy the convenience of being just a stone's throw away from schools and shopping , making daily errands a breeze. Experience the charm of Memphis, surrounded by scenic landscapes and a sense of community. Enjoy the serenity of a peaceful neighborhood while having the convenience of essential amenities within reach. Metal Roof: Stylish and durable, the metal roof adds a modern touch to the classic charm of this home. Generous Garage: A spacious garage provides ample room for your vehicles, storage, or a workshop – the possibilities are endless! With all appliances included, you can start creating memories in your new home from day one. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Disclaimer: All information provided is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed and should be independently verified.
